Third-party components
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This software bundles or builds against CUTLASS (NVIDIA, BSD-3-Clause) and
stb_image (Sean Barrett, MIT or Public Domain), and reimplements algorithms
adapted via DVLT from DINOv2, PyTorch3D, MoGe, MultiNeRF, Depth-Anything-3, and
AnyCalib. See THIRD_PARTY.md for full attribution and license texts.
